  "description": "Gran Marbella Views!\n\nIntroducing a charming 2-bedroom apartment with stunning views in arguably the very best location in Marbella. Sitting in the heart of Marbella, this cozy retreat offers an unparalleled coastal living experience.\n\nAs you step into the apartment, you're greeted by an atmosphere of soothing comfort. The apartment features a spacious layout with fresh colours, furnishings and decor, creating a stylish yet inviting ambiance. From the living room, kitchen, terrace and bedrooms you will be overwhelmed by the wonderful views of the sea and Marbella's golden mile boardwalk.\n\nThe apartment features 2 bedrooms with one en-suite bathroom. It steps out onto the balcony and practically allows you to wake up with the view of the Mediterranean. The two bedrooms feature double beds.\n\nThe highlight of this stunning residence is its private terrace, where you can unwind and soak in the Mediterranean sunshine while enjoying breathtaking views of the communal gardens, sparkling swimming pool, and the azure waters of the Mediterranean sea.\n\nGran Marbella Seafront Residence boasts a prime location as the complex offers direct access to the picturesque paseo, a charming promenade that leads directly to the beach. Whether you're in the mood for a leisurely stroll along the coastline or a refreshing dip in the sea, the convenience of beachfront living is right at your doorstep.\n\nSurrounded by an array of shops, bars, cafes and restaurants, Gran Marbella Oasis offers easy access to a vibrant dining and entertainment scene. Explore the culinary delights of Marbella's renowned restaurants or indulge in a shopping spree at nearby boutiques and markets.\n\nWith its unbeatable location, number of amenities, and captivating views, Gran Marbella Marina is the perfect choice for those seeking a fun by day and cozy by night coastal retreat in Marbella.\n\nPlease note that we welcome families and couples only, no groups under 30, and no hen or stag parties. Should you fall outside of this category but wish to book nonetheless, please send us an enquiry detailing a bit more about yourself and the group that you will be travelling with so we can request this for you.\n\nWe look forward to welcoming you!",
